description:
Today's actions shape tomorrow's world. Which is why, here at DICOTA, we are dedicated to developing environmentally friendly solutions and therefore make all the items in our ECO collections out of sustainable, recycled PET. We reuse up to 19 PET bottles, so you will receive an environmentally friendly product with a life-long guarantee. Our PET products also have the quality, look and finish that you know and love.


The compact Eco Multi BASE case offers ideal protection for your laptop thanks to its padded notebook compartment. The case fully protects devices between 14 and 15.6" and the elastic strap also secures them within their compartment. The Eco Multi BASE guarantees extra stability and protection with its metal frame, as well as flexible mobility thanks to its lightweight design. Your smartphone or other smaller items like cables, pens or chargers can be stored in the convenient front pocket, so they are always to hand. The case's handles make it comfortable to carry and it can be attached to a suitcase in seconds with its built-in strap. It can also be carried using its adjustable shoulder strap. The Eco Multi BASE is therefore perfect for you if you always on the go and want to support the recycling of PET bottles with an eco-friendly case.

  • Notebook security strap

name: Laptop Backpack MOVE 13-15.6"
shortDescription:
• Notebook compartment cushioned with High Density Foam (HDF) & padded slip pocket for tablets up to 10.5 inches
  • YKK Quick & Easy Lock System
  • Side pocket for power bank to charge your smartphone on the go
description:
From yoga classes to the office. MOVE is designed for daily use. Comfortable thanks to its ergonomic back cushioning and cushioned shoulder straps with an adjustable chest belt. Perfectly manoeuvre your backpack thanks to the two handles for carrying. The fabric is made of water-repellent materials but in case of thunderstorms, the backpack also includes a rain cover with a reflective DICOTA logo. The primary storage area contains a notebook compartment cushioned with High Density Foam (HDF), a padded slip pocket for tablets up to 10.5 inches, a divider for documents and an elastic mesh pocket to hold your drink bottle. The second main compartment contains dividers for headphones and folders.


Enjoy the bag's functional details everywhere you go. The Backpack MOVE features two adjustable straps at the front that can hold a yoga mat or a jacket. The two front pockets can be used to store accessories such as pens, charging cables or smartphones. The right-hand side pocket (looking at the backpack from the front) is designed to charge your devices on the go. Place your power bank inside and connect to your phone. The pocket on the left-hand side can be used for quick access to water bottles, umbrellas and key cards. This backpack comes with the Quick & Easy Lock System form YKK. This system easily locks the zippers, securing your backpack in seconds. Pull the two zippers together to lock them, or unlock them by pulling the sliders down into the lower plastic part. The backpack is available in two colours.

  • Notebook compartment cushioned with High Density Foam (HDF) & padded slip pocket for tablets up to 10.5 inches
  • YKK Quick & Easy Lock System
  • Side pocket for power bank to charge your smartphone on the go
  • Adjustable straps at the front for jackets, yoga mats, etc.
  • Ergonomic back cushioning
  • Cushioned shoulder straps including adjustable chest belt

description:
Stylish and functional, this original daypack holds your gym and work essentials. The Backpack GO is comfortable to carry thanks to its ergonomic back cushioning and padded shoulder straps with an adjustable chest belt. Also includes a handle for carrying. The open front compartment expands easily to fit anything you need. Store your computer and documents in the notebook compartment cushioned with High Density Foam (HDF). The compartment is hidden in the back panel to provide perfect anti-theft protection. The main compartment contains one divider for tablets or documents and a zipped pocket for headphones. The spacious front compartments have a workstation for a pen and small items, such as power banks or charging cables. The backpack has a large front pocket and a loop to attach a bike LED light for when you cycle. Last but not least, there are two mesh pockets on the sides for drink bottles and umbrellas. Available in two colours.

description:
Lived sustainability with a clear conscience - the accessories pouches MOVE are manufactured from recycled PET and are kind to the environment. Consistent recycling helps to conserve resources. At DICOTA, it's the foundation of our innovative solutions. Within the main material of the pouch, 3 PET bottles are given a new life - without compromising on quality, functionality or design. The bag offers excellent protection for your devices and is comfortable and easy to carry. Designed for daily use. Equipped with practical functions that make your life easier.


Passport, ticket, smartphone, charger, cables, power bank, adapter, headphones, keys, gaming console, games, controller and more. With the Accessories Pouch MOVE you enjoy carefree travelling, knowing that all your belongings are perfectly organized and always within reach. The sophisticated interior with a variation of pockets, zipper compartments and flexible fixation straps provides storage space for everything you cannot miss during your journey. The RFID lined zipper compartment protects against unwanted scans, ensuring that your cards and personal information remain private and confidential. When travelling on a plane, use the key-holder as a hanger to attach the pouch to the seat in front of you and thereby safe space to comfortably rest your legs. Besides its great functionality, the pouch convinces as well in terms of design and durability thanks to an exciting combination of high-quality Polyester materials made from recycled PET.

name: Laptop Case Slim Eco PRO 12-14.1"
shortDescription:
• Lockable and cushioned notebook compartment with fitall system and anti slip technology
  • Maximum security thanks to Memory Foam and EVA frame protection
  • Cushioned pocket for tablets up to 10.5"
description:
Today's actions shape tomorrow's world. Which is why, here at DICOTA, we are dedicated to developing environmentally friendly solutions and therefore make all the items in our ECO collections out of sustainable, recycled PET. We reuse up to 36 PET bottles, so you will receive an environmentally friendly product with a life-long guarantee. Our PET products also have the quality, look and finish that you know and love.


The Eco Slim Case PRO reliably accompanies you everywhere and meets the highest standards in terms of quality, functionality and protection. The fitall system separating wall in the notebook compartment lies protectively around your device and fits automatically to sizes from 12-14.1". The perforated and thus light EVA foam material optimally protects the edges of your notebook. The high-quality genuine leather handles ensure comfortable transportation for daily use. Besides the notebook compartment, the Eco Slim Case PRO features a well-padded slip pocket designated to tablets up to 10.5". Furthermore, the bag offers generous storage space for documents at the back of the case. The front pocket allows you to organize your personal equipment and additional mobile accessories. With its trolley fastening strap, the Eco Slim Case PRO ensures perfect comfort when travelling along with luggage. The Eco Slim Case PRO is perfect for you if you are always on the go and want to support the recycling of PET bottles with an eco-friendly case.

  • Made of 7.5 recycled PET bottles
  • Lockable and cushioned notebook compartment with fitall system and anti slip technology
  • Maximum security thanks to Memory Foam and EVA frame protection
  • Cushioned pocket for tablets up to 10.5"
  • Spacious front pocket with zip-pocket and workstation for mobile accessories
  • Open document compartment on the rear
  • High-quality metal features
  • Adjustable shoulder strap with comfortable padding and anti slip technology
  • Comfortable carry handles made of real leather
  • Trolley belt
